Mariah O'Brien https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mariah_O%27Brien 0 Mariah Waterfall O'Brien (born June 25, 1971) is an American interior designer and former actress and model. She made her film debut in the drama Gas, Food, Lodging (1992) and later appeared in the horror film Halloween: The Curse of Michael Myers (1995). O'Brien also appeared on the cover of Alice in Chains's 1992 album Dirt. Mariah_Waterfall_O'Brien ( born June_25_,_1971 ) is an_American_interior_designer and former_actress_and_model .
